      "writtenOn": "2026-06-26T19:49:21Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "What is the reason for switching from `getter.py` script to other solution? Is it for complicated parsing of test results, performance or some other reason? `getter.py` already uses multi-threading and also reusing single session.",
      "revId": "f93b4fdbaf6d27c90cfcc29e10f5bebe8b6a6bee",
      "serverId": "7fc14799-209e-464c-9743-7a06c2c21a81"
